WEBVTT

00:05:27.284 --> 00:05:30.024
"How does a bird fly
differently than I flew

00:05:30.048 --> 00:05:31.255
when I was a bat?"

00:05:32.627 --> 00:05:35.930
The digital technology prompted
embodied learning

00:05:35.954 --> 00:05:38.585
that kids can now take out into the world.

00:05:40.361 --> 00:05:42.753
Fear number two:

00:05:43.927 --> 00:05:46.999
"Playing games on these screens
is just a waste of time.

00:05:47.023 --> 00:05:49.825
It's going to distract children
from their education."

00:05:52.007 --> 00:05:53.408
Game developers know

00:05:53.432 --> 00:05:55.842
that you can learn a lot
about a player's skill

00:05:55.866 --> 00:05:57.944
by looking at the back-end data:

00:05:57.968 --> 00:06:00.282
Where did a player pause?